{"data": [{"id": "4743481", "title": "New Administration Motivates Fresh Look At International Investments", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A world globe marked with several national flag pins\" data-id=\"1303046106\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5220px\" height=\"3480px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Brian Manby, CFA</em></p> <p>Few assets garnered more attention following the U.S. presidential election than the dollar, and for good reason.</p> <p>The incoming Trump administration has advocated for tariffs to challenge existing U.S. trade relationships. Most of this rhetoric has</p>", "image": "https: