inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Quarterly review </h2> <p>The fund underperformed its benchmark, the MSCI Emerging Markets ('EM') Index (Net), over the three-month and 12-month periods that ended September 30, 2024.</p> <p> The largest contributors to quarterly performance included China, Taiwan, consumer discretionary, and consumer staples, while the largest</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2163730037/image_2163730037.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743480-allspring-emerging-markets-equity-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 09:35:00"}, {"id": "4743474", "title": "APA Still Weighed Down (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dusk shot of an oil Fracking Drill Rig Under Dramatic Sunset Sky in the Permian Basin in West Texas or New Mexico\" data-id=\"1438198947\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">grandriver</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I previously reviewed APA Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/APA\" title=\"APA Corporation\">APA</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4694778-why-apa-corporation-stock-is-a-bargain-now-rating-upgrade\">in May 2024</a> and am now downranking it from buy to hold. APA\u2019s production is either in challenged/slow markets (Permian dry gas whose price dips below zero) or is in what has become</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1438198947/image_1438198947.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743474-apa-still-weighed-down", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 09:25:24"}, {"id": "4743472", "title": "Masimo: A Stellar Performance After The Dust Has Settled", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Two mouths arguing with speech bubbles and graphic symbols in between them\" data-id=\"2149257032\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Over the summer, I believed that a bitter and intense proxy fight was hurting management and shares, and thereby investors, in <strong>Masimo (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MASI\" title=\"Masimo Corporation\">MASI</a></span>)</strong>. After the company was contemplating reversing the Sound United acquisition, a fight</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2149257032/image_2149257032.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743472-masimo-stellar-performance-after-dust-settled", "pub_date": "2024-12-11 09:00:09"}, {"id": "4743475", "title": "Artisan International Small-Mid Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322454835/image_1322454835.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Close up coins on table background and saving money and business growth concept, Finance and investment concept, Money coin stack growing graph, advertising coins of finance and banking\" data-id=\"1322454835\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\"